headline: WillScot to nominate Dominick Zarcone as independent director
summary: WillScot (WSC) Holdings announced that, as part of its ongoing board refreshment efforts, the WillScot Board of Directors has unanimously approved the nomination of Dominick Zarcone to stand for election to the Board at the Company’s 2025 Annual Meeting of Stockholders. The Board has also unanimously determined that Worthing Jackman will assume the role of non-executive, independent Chairman to succeed Erik Olsson, who will be retiring from the Board following the Annual Meeting.
